It includes monthly and annual summaries of electricity (kWh), demand (kW), gas (therms), and steam (MLBs) usage, along with their respective costs. The table also captures metadata about the buildings, such as building type and agency information.

The complexity of this table is high due to its extensive number of columns, which cover multiple metrics across two fiscal years. The table's structure is wide, with numerous columns dedicated to monthly and annual summaries for different types of energy consumption and costs. This complexity is further increased by the lack of explicit primary keys and foreign keys, which complicates data integrity and relational mapping.
